January 26,2020.

The second day of the first lunar month.

Day 4 of the city closure in Wuhan.

The third day the gate of Heaven is closed.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Tear resistance. Cars aren't allowed on the road anymore, so we all stay at home together. There used to be a joke about giving you a room, food, cell phone, Wi fi, but you couldn't go out and see how long you could stay? Surprise, the joke became a reality in 2020. Just don't limit yourself to one room: If you get tired of lying in bed, you can go for a walk in the living room, take a look at the view from the balcony, and walk around in a pair of pajamas to the hottest spots during this year's Spring Festival holiday. What's more, it has taken the responsibility for the country and contributed to the society! The only side effect is probably weight gain. Then I'm out of balance. Why eat so much every day and not gain weight? Hmm?

Was also "sealed" away from the Wuhan 100 km of the epidemic area, brush the front of the first-hand News, still thinking about her, the safety and security. I repeatedly in the struggle, if at that time trapped in Wuhan can not come back, how is this good? Is it a tragedy or a comedy? After all, I was the gate of Heaven that closed the city of Wuhan (No. 23) the day before. On the evening of the 21st, when Academician Zhong Nanshan led his team in Wuhan to release the news of the COVID-19's passing from man to man, after the whole country was shocked, I even went on a whim to find a girlfriend. We can shoot a Vlog tomorrow, from the source of the South China Seafood Market to the Hankou Railway Station to Golden Pond Hospital and other important places around, record the scene. The next day and a discussion, considering the afternoon to return to Tianmen, time is too short, the script is not mature, the atmosphere is more and more tense, feel the risk is quite big, not done.

Selfie with a girlfriend 20200122 in Wuchang

Back home the next day, that is, the first day of the city of Wuhan, Ma Zizhuan I this video, said you see, millions of views. I said okay. Of course, our original intention is not to fire ah how, but in order to have already begun to demonize Wuhan's out-of-town Basin friends to see, "epidemic area" the true face. I believe you have seen, Lin Chen teacher this is also a great record, it is worth our learning. I've had a few reporters follow up, and I've been keeping an eye on them.
